<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 12:13:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“街上没人认识我。但我因为写的东西而收到了死亡威胁”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-06-20/ty-article/.highlight/no-one-recognizes-me-on-the-street-but-i-have-gotten-death-threats-for-things-i-wrote/00000190-3564-d6fa-abb4-77ef9e4e0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名作家在以色列面临着作为一名创意人员的高潮和低谷，而一名男孩则在两个国家都有家</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 12:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-06-20/ty-article/.highlight/no-one-recognizes-me-on-the-street-but-i-have-gotten-death-threats-for-things-i-wrote/00000190-3564-d6fa-abb4-77ef9e4e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将就国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡和加兰特的逮捕令请求支付 32,000 美元的律师费</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-pays-32-000-in-legal-fees-for-iccs-arrest-warrant-requests-for-israeli-leaders/00000190-34f6-d690-a190-f4f723980000</link><description>国际刑事法院检察官上个月因加沙战争向以色列总理内塔尼亚胡和国防部长约阿夫·加兰特提出逮捕令后，以色列国将向两名律师支付 12 万谢克尔的律师费</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 10:19:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-pays-32-000-in-legal-fees-for-iccs-arrest-warrant-requests-for-israeli-leaders/00000190-34f6-d690-a190-f4f723980000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长不会代表司法部长任命他选择的最高法院院长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/ag-will-not-represent-justice-minister-in-his-bid-to-appoint-a-supreme-court-president/00000190-349f-d690-a190-f49f3c050000</link><description>虽然以色列司法改革的设计者试图废除最高法院院长的资历制度，但以色列总检察长认为应该保留这一制度——它保证了法院的独立性，并将政治与任命过程分开</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 09:57:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/ag-will-not-represent-justice-minister-in-his-bid-to-appoint-a-supreme-court-president/00000190-349f-d690-a190-f49f3c050000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长禁止内塔尼亚胡任命下一任公务员专员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israels-attorney-general-bars-netanyahu-from-appointing-next-civil-service-commissioner/00000190-347b-d5f5-a5d6-fdfba4620000</link><description>据称现任公务员专员滥用该部门的权力为内塔尼亚胡服务并在政治上清洗公务员队伍，以色列总检察长裁定总理内塔尼亚胡不能直接任命下一任专员</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 08:05:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israels-attorney-general-bars-netanyahu-from-appointing-next-civil-service-commissioner/00000190-347b-d5f5-a5d6-fdfba4620000</guid></item><item><title>红海敌对行动因加沙战争而爆发，但即使在战争结束后也可能继续下去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/red-sea-hostilities-erupted-because-of-the-gaza-war-but-could-go-on-even-after-it-ends/00000190-32a9-d39e-a999-76ef6c170000</link><description>美国官员认为，红海袭击符合胡塞武装领导人的政治利益，胡塞武装领导人寻求提高自己的地区声誉，同时继续获得伊朗的援助</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 03:00:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/red-sea-hostilities-erupted-because-of-the-gaza-war-but-could-go-on-even-after-it-ends/00000190-32a9-d39e-a999-76ef6c170000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射了 10 多枚火箭弹；以色列国防军在西岸逮捕九人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article-live/nasrallah-threatens-israel-cyprus-idf-chief-hezbollah-unaware-of-all-our-capabilities/00000190-3369-d700-a7f0-bfebd8230000</link><description>官员称，美国军方停止启动的加沙码头将恢复运营 ■ 宗教服务部长表示，由于以色列北部可能发生战争，该部正在为集体埋葬做好准备 ■ 中央司令部表示，它袭击了也门胡塞武装控制地区的目标 ■ 美国取消内塔尼亚胡批评拜登政府后与以色列就伊朗问题举行战略会议</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 02:21:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article-live/nasrallah-threatens-israel-cyprus-idf-chief-hezbollah-unaware-of-all-our-capabilities/00000190-3369-d700-a7f0-bfebd8230000</guid></item><item><title>误报和疲劳：以色列军队在拉法英勇作战，但“全面胜利”仍遥不可及</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-troops-battle-bravely-in-rafah-as-total-victory-remains-elusive/00000190-3222-d340-a1f8-3a26cfaf0000</link><description>“我们将在几周内击败拉法的哈马斯部队，”在加沙作战的纳哈尔旅指挥官说。但他承认，许多恐怖分子已逃离该市，寻找人质并不是他在那里的任务的一部分</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 22:38:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-troops-battle-bravely-in-rafah-as-total-victory-remains-elusive/00000190-3222-d340-a1f8-3a26cfaf0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党领导人威胁称，如果战斗升级，将入侵以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-chief-threatens-to-invade-israel-if-fighting-escalates/00000190-3221-d340-a1f8-3a25f9c00000</link><description>纳斯鲁拉在电视讲话中还指责塞浦路斯允许以色列军队使用其机场和基地进行训练</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 21:56:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-chief-threatens-to-invade-israel-if-fighting-escalates/00000190-3221-d340-a1f8-3a25f9c00000</guid></item><item><title>坚持比比还是跳槽？正统派的困境将决定内塔尼亚胡的命运</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/stick-with-bibi-or-jump-ship-the-haredi-dilemma-that-will-seal-netanyahus-fate/00000190-31da-d39e-a999-77debbea0000</link><description>正统派已经从内塔尼亚胡那里得到了一切，但与总理不同的是，他只会留下焦土，正统派领导人德里和加夫尼对他们的社区负有责任</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 20:29:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/stick-with-bibi-or-jump-ship-the-haredi-dilemma-that-will-seal-netanyahus-fate/00000190-31da-d39e-a999-77debbea0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争让以色列陷入困境，内塔尼亚胡的疯狂和狂妄自大得到充分展现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/as-gaza-war-bogs-israel-down-netanyahus-madness-and-megalomania-are-on-full-display/00000190-2f9c-d700-a7f0-affe48be0000</link><description>甘茨离开后，战时内阁可能已经解散，但内塔尼亚胡领导的掠夺者内阁并没有浪费时间</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 19:48:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/as-gaza-war-bogs-israel-down-netanyahus-madness-and-megalomania-are-on-full-display/00000190-2f9c-d700-a7f0-affe48be0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔说，他的以色列警察局长候选人毕业于弗吉尼亚大学。他没有</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-says-his-candidate-for-israel-police-chief-graduated-from-uva-he-didnt/00000190-31cd-d5f5-a5d6-f9ef1a2f0000</link><description>国家安全部长写道，Avshalom Peled 是“弗吉尼亚大学犯罪学项目的毕业生”，但《国土报》发现他在该机构的学习包括 1987 年为期六周、15 小时的 FBI 课程</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 19:42:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-says-his-candidate-for-israel-police-chief-graduated-from-uva-he-didnt/00000190-31cd-d5f5-a5d6-f9ef1a2f0000</guid></item><item><title>医院和大学工作人员在以色列警察袭击后抗议，并在反政府集会上逮捕医生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/hospital-workers-protest-after-israel-police-assault-arrest-doctors-at-anti-govt-rally/00000190-312a-d340-a1f8-392ec0970000</link><description>警察在治疗受伤的抗议者时袭击了一名医生并逮捕了另一名医生。医生们称这些事件“跨越了双方商定的界限”，这可能导致工作人员“出于对自身安全的恐惧”而拒绝在现场提供医疗服务</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 19:03:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/hospital-workers-protest-after-israel-police-assault-arrest-doctors-at-anti-govt-rally/00000190-312a-d340-a1f8-392ec0970000</guid></item><item><title>“不受欢迎”：以色列侨民团体发起运动，要求撤销内塔尼亚胡国会邀请</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/non-grata-israeli-expats-launch-campaign-to-get-netanyahu-congress-invite-rescinded/00000190-31a2-d4fa-ad9d-ffab47550000</link><description>UnXeptable 是一个领导了以色列侨民在全球举行的许多反内塔尼亚胡抗议活动的组织，如果内塔尼亚胡向国会发表讲话的邀请不被撤回，该组织打算在内塔尼亚胡讲话期间将一车的以色列裔美国人带到国会外抗议</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 18:12:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/non-grata-israeli-expats-launch-campaign-to-get-netanyahu-congress-invite-rescinded/00000190-31a2-d4fa-ad9d-ffab47550000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡表示，以色列国防军对摧毁哈马斯表示怀疑，以色列军队“有义务”实现政府设定的目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/netanyahu-says-army-obligated-to-goals-set-by-govt-after-idf-doubts-hamas-destruction/00000190-316e-d340-a1f8-396e91ac0000</link><description>以色列军方发言人丹尼尔·哈加里 (Daniel Hagari) 表示，“任何认为我们能够消灭哈马斯的人都是错误的”，因为政治领导人和以色列国防军领导人之间的紧张局势因加沙战斗的延长而持续加剧</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 17:47:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/netanyahu-says-army-obligated-to-goals-set-by-govt-after-idf-doubts-hamas-destruction/00000190-316e-d340-a1f8-396e91ac0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔和内塔尼亚胡互相嘲笑，总理恳求联盟伙伴“控制住”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-netanyahu-trade-jeers-as-pm-implores-coalition-partners-to-get-a-grip/00000190-3075-d39e-a999-76ff6afd0000</link><description>本-格维尔、内塔尼亚胡和德里周二因试图确保政府对市政拉比任命拥有控制权的法案获得多数席位而产生分歧，随后发生冲突。该法案于周三被废除</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 17:32:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-netanyahu-trade-jeers-as-pm-implores-coalition-partners-to-get-a-grip/00000190-3075-d39e-a999-76ff6afd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 257 天：发言人称那些认为以色列国防军可以摧毁哈马斯的人是错误的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-257-those-who-think-idf-can-destroy-hamas-are-mistaken-spokesman-says/00000190-316e-dc02-a7d8-f17e7ec40000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡指责拜登推迟运送武器后，白宫取消了与以色列就伊朗问题举行的重要战略会议 ■ 以色列国家审计长表示，总理办公室要求他推迟对其 10 月 7 日前后行为的调查 ■ 约 25 枚火箭从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射 ■ 联合国：无法由于加沙人的无法无天和恐慌，从加沙边境口岸分发援助物资 ■ 这是战争进入 257 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 17:04:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-257-those-who-think-idf-can-destroy-hamas-are-mistaken-spokesman-says/00000190-316e-dc02-a7d8-f17e7ec40000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列定居者因用斧头袭击西岸巴勒斯坦家庭而被判入狱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-settlers-sentenced-to-prison-for-axe-attack-on-palestinian-family-in-west-bank/00000190-30ed-d39e-a999-76ef1a470000</link><description>这两名定居者因在 2023 年胡瓦拉骚乱期间出于种族动机袭击五名家庭成员并破坏汽车而被判处三年监禁。两人承认了对他们提出的指控</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 17:01:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-settlers-sentenced-to-prison-for-axe-attack-on-palestinian-family-in-west-bank/00000190-30ed-d39e-a999-76ef1a470000</guid></item><item><title>拜登还需要多少证据来证明内塔尼亚胡不是美国盟友？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.highlight/how-much-more-proof-does-biden-need-that-netanyahu-is-not-a-u-s-ally/00000190-30e8-d4fa-ad9d-ffe94ffa0000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡在这段令人翻白眼的视频中指责美国人扣押了一批军火，并再次让人想起了温斯顿·丘吉尔，这是他在玩弄政治——这是他唯一知道该怎么做的事情。他七月份在国会发表讲话的邀请应该推迟到美国大选之后</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 15:45:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.highlight/how-much-more-proof-does-biden-need-that-netanyahu-is-not-a-u-s-ally/00000190-30e8-d4fa-ad9d-ffe94ffa0000</guid></item><item><title>“许多犹太人表示，如果极右或极左赢得选举，他们将离开法国”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-19/ty-article-podcast/many-jews-say-theyll-leave-france-if-the-far-right-or-extreme-left-win-the-election/00000190-2fe3-dc02-a7d8-eff7030c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 15:21:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-19/ty-article-podcast/many-jews-say-theyll-leave-france-if-the-far-right-or-extreme-left-win-the-election/00000190-2fe3-dc02-a7d8-eff7030c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列表示计划建立一个替代红十字会的机构来探视巴勒斯坦囚犯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-planning-to-establish-alternative-to-red-cross-for-visits-to-palestinian-prisoners/00000190-30d3-d700-a7f0-bdf388410000</link><description>自加沙战争爆发以来，红十字会已停止探视被关押在以色列的巴勒斯坦人。以色列没有提供替代机制的细节，但国土报了解到，一个选择是法官和外国外交官的访问。以色列民权组织称此举违反国际法</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 15:08:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-planning-to-establish-alternative-to-red-cross-for-visits-to-palestinian-prisoners/00000190-30d3-d700-a7f0-bdf388410000</guid></item></channel></rss>